Another CR door opened up as Needlenose came out, all spic and span.  "HAh right on dude, this rules" he said looking at how shiny he was.  Nightmares smoke began to flow over him.  "Woh woh, dream boy, you fog is making a smidge on my new polish, watch it..."

Dreadwing sped over the Pacific Ocean then overNorth America.  He noticed a small battle going on below.  "Let Investigate" Dreadwind, part of DReadwing, said to his counterpart.  "All right" the answer from DArkwing came.  "Then get off my ass" The two seperated creating two small jets and flew down, imedialtly noticing Shockwave.  They flew down and landed behind them.  Dread wind spoke "Shockwave, are you member of a Decepticon faction here on Earth"
